  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The TAXUS ARRIVE study is a multi-center safety and surveillance study designed to to compile
      safety surveillance and clinical outcomes data for the TAXUS™ Express2™ Paclitaxel-Eluting
      Coronary Stent System in routine clinical practice and to identify low frequency TAXUS
      related clinical events.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
